Package com.google.inject.tools.suite.snippets.problems

Classes representing problems that can occur when running Guice code.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
CodeProblem.CodeProblemVisitor  
 

Class Summary
BadClassProblem Represents a ClassNotFoundException.
BindingProblem Represents a problem with a binding.
CodeProblem Represents a problem found involving the user's guice code, such as a CreationException.
CreationProblem Represents a CreationException.
InjectorProblem Represents a problem creating an injector.
InvalidModuleProblem Represents a problem that a module being used is not vaid.
KeyProblem Represents a problem with a Guice key.
LocationProblem Represents a problem finding the location of a binding.
OutOfScopeProblem Represents an OutOfScopeException.
ScopeProblem Represents a problem finding the scope of a binding.
